title: Flor de las Antillas by My Father Cigars
itunes:title: Flor de las Antillas by My Father Cigars
description: We're smoking Cigar Aficionado's Cigar of the Year, Flor de las Antillas by My Father Cigars with their Northeast Area Sales Manager Jeremy Soares. We also pick apart and discuss other Cigar's of the Year, and give you our opinion and yours!
